{"metadata":{"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"headers:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"headers"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Enterprise security","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Regional compliance"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network monitoring"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Firewall restrictions","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"while preserving all headers and request body content.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"title":"PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}]}}}